name: Visions of Flight by Ducks of a Feather

metadata.name: Visions of Flight #1
metadata.description: Division Street and its Ducks of a Feather platform present Visions of Flight, 7200 one-of-a-kind NFTs will be minted with 5000 being sold to financially benefit participating University of Oregon women student-athletes. Each of the NFTs was designed by artist Lili Tae in collaboration with Sedona Prince and multiple women student-athletes across a wide range of sports.
